<h5 id="devereux-2000-famine-in-the-20th-century"> <a class="deep-link" href="#devereux-2000-famine-in-the-20th-century"># </a>Devereux (2000) Famine in the 20th Century</h5>
<ul>
<li><strong>Data:</strong> Famines with mortality above 1,000 deaths.</li>
<li><strong>Geographical coverage:</strong> Global</li>
<li><strong>Time span:</strong> 1900-2000</li>
<li><strong>Available at:</strong> The research paper Devereux (2000) â Famine in the 20th century is published as a IDS Working Paper <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171208231529/http://www.ids.ac.uk/publication/famine-in-the-twentieth-century">here</a>.<a id="ref-45" class="side-matter side-matter-ref" href="#note-45"><sup class="side-matter side-matter-sup" title="The reference is Devereux (2000) â Famine in the 20th century. IDS Working Paper 105. Brighton: Institute for Development Studies">45</sup></a></li>
</ul>
