<h5 id="world-peace-foundation-famine-trends-dataset"> <a class="deep-link" href="#world-peace-foundation-famine-trends-dataset"># </a>World Peace Foundation, Famine Trends Dataset</h5>
<ul>
<li><strong>Data:</strong> Famines with mortality above 100,000 deaths and episodes of mass intentional starvation with killed more than 10,000</li>
<li><strong>Geographical coverage:</strong> Global</li>
<li><strong>Time span:</strong> 1870-present</li>
<li><strong>Available at: </strong>the World Peace Foundation website <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171208231529/http://fletcher.tufts.edu/World-Peace-Foundation/Program/Research/Mass-Atrocities-Research-Program/Mass-Famine#Dataset.">here</a>.</li>
</ul>
